{subhead} DDE News{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

We have return from vacations and now we are
ready to bring you some news regarding our work.
{p} {p}
10.09.1999.{p}
Wasted Dreams online registration
{p} {p}
From now on it is possible to register our products
online too. Simply choose registration button from
the left menu (on our web site).
{p} {p}
As a registered user you'll get discounts on our
future releases, as well as some other privileges.
{p} {p}
Thanks to all that have submitted their registration
cards. We'll contact all of you through email to
confirm your registration. If you don't receive our
email in a couple of days please contact us at
contact@dd-ent.com
{p} {p}
10.09.1999.{p}
Diablo's Land new screenshots. 
{p} {p}
We have converted all the background graphics to High
resolution and now we are processing characters and
additional graphics (weapons, spells, shields, etc.).
{p} {p}
Each week we will post a new screenshot from the game
to Diablo's Land web page (choose games from the left
menu then Diablo's Land), so you can see the progress
of the game and tell us your opinion, comments or
suggestions (please use comment form on Diablo's Land
web page).
{p} {p}
Here's one teasing news (only for our news subscribers.)
{p} {p}
We are negotiating (almost done) with one (still confidential
information) developing team to purchase their unfinished game
(also confidential) to improve it and finish it.
{p} {p}
We'll have more information's about this next week (along with
screenshots and probably game demo).
{p} {p}
Regards,{p}
Raymond{p}
Digital Dreams Entertainment{p}
